s/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T18:48:06.000Z","msg":"後生當然跑得快<br />\n但係隨年紀增長<br />\n身體機能係會減退<br />\n以前跑到1000米 唔代表4050歳仲可以跑到1000米<br />\n需要互相理解 互補長短<br />\n小批評多做事<br />\n場運動其實團結左香港人<br />\n以前既香港人好冷漠<br />\n依家都有義載<br />\n亦見唔小真係順路三唔識七都車哂去一個地方"},{"pid":"0588ae8816950de4121442b03e16f61a0ab730bd","tid":1830610,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T18:53:39.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好忘記<br />\n點解我地可以走得咁遠<br />\n團結就係我地最大既武器同防護<br />\n每一個同路人 都係我地團隊最珍貴既資源<br />\n缺一不可 同時希望大家愛惜生命<br />\n一齊行落去"},{"pid":"0a1287f27c84d84952696665d9faa8ffd5cd68ac","tid":1830610,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T18:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8bb3a117178552a25b3b5b23cd695a05a20bdc9","tid":1830610,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T19:05:42.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n上面個Post屌完走得快<br />\n下面個Post就屌走得慢<br />\n<br />\n冇獨立思考嘅人睇得多連登真係會精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03387edfce77564ebb34f8f9f438b5a9560ac57e","tid":1830610,"uid":34424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T19:12:47.000Z","msg":"其實講真而家帶裝真係冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> poly之後跟本打唔到陣地 人哋未放tg已經捉人/放完冇耐圍捕 帶裝反而仲大風險"},{"pid":"b63396b6703a5e037abd4563b37245dffae9d6fb","tid":1830610,"uid":252311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T19:13:11.000Z","msg":"身邊有朋友直情因爲咁而唔上連登"},{"pid":"ff771aeac33faedb029083e1370b9e9ec1a17b90","tid":1830610,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T19:19:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc666c4c87b7c471ae3acf02d0bd15e6645870a","tid":1830610,"uid":4